He's just really banged up.

348
00:30:00,632 --> 00:30:03,593
Oh, look at his poor little feet.

349
00:30:06,846 --> 00:30:09,432
Hang in there, buddy. 
You're gonna be all right.

350
00:30:10,809 --> 00:30:14,187
- So, this is it? 
- That's it. That's your pyramid.

351
00:30:14,270 --> 00:30:16,356
Wow, look at that thing!

352
00:30:16,439 --> 00:30:17,607
What happens now?

353
00:30:18,483 --> 00:30:21,110
- Oh. He's... gone. 
- Yep.

354
00:30:22,445 --> 00:30:24,822
